# OGP Agent Scheduler Tasks File
# This file contains scheduled tasks that the OGP Agent will execute
# Format: minute hour day_of_month month day_of_week command
# 
# Examples:
# 0 2 * * * echo "Daily maintenance task at 2 AM"
# */30 * * * * echo "Task runs every 30 minutes"
# 0 0 * * 0 echo "Weekly task on Sunday at midnight"
#
# Special OGP actions can be used with %ACTION= prefix:
# 0 6 * * * %ACTION=start|%|home_id|%|server_args...
# 0 22 * * * %ACTION=stop|%|home_id|%|ip|%|port|%|...
# 0 12 * * * %ACTION=restart|%|home_id|%|...
#
# Resource stats collection is automatically scheduled if database is configured
# Additional custom tasks can be added below:
